<% layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/privacy.css">
<section class="privacy-page-full">
    <h1 class="privacy-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="privacy-date">Last updated: June 5, 2025</p>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Tripify. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you use our services through our platform.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and password.</li>
            <li><strong>Booking Details:</strong> Stay dates, guest count, and property preferences.</li>
            <li><strong>Device Info:</strong> IP address, browser type, and device identifiers.</li>
            <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> To remember login sessions and analyze usage.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Process bookings and payments securely.</li>
            <li>Improve our website and services.</li>
            <li>Send confirmations, alerts, and offers (with consent).</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>4. Sharing Your Data</h2>
        <p>We may share your information with:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Hosts or property owners for booking purposes.</li>
            <li>Third-party service providers like payment processors.</li>
            <li>Authorities if legally required.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement strong security measures (SSL, encryption, limited access) to protect your data. However, no online method is 100% secure.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You can request access to your data, ask for corrections, or request deletion at any time by emailing <a href="mailto:privacy@tripify.com">privacy@tripify.com</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions or feedback about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@tripify.com">support@tripify.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
</section>
